I"<p>자바스크립트 내장 메소드를 사용하여 문자열을 거꾸로 뒤집어볼까?</p>

<div class="language-javascript highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kd">let</span> <span class="nx">str</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">태촌이는 공부중</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">;</span>

<span class="nx">str</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">str</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">split</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">""</span><span class="p">);</span> <span class="c1">// 문자열 -&gt; 배열</span>
<span class="nx">str</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">str</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">reverse</span><span class="p">();</span> <span class="c1">// 배열 거꾸로 뒤집기</span>
<span class="nx">str</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nx">str</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">join</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">""</span><span class="p">);</span> <span class="c1">// 배열 -&gt; 문자열</span>

<span class="nx">console</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">log</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">str</span><span class="p">);</span> <span class="c1">// "중부공 는이촌태"</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

